title: Dishwasher VENT ASMY, BLOWER
description: Dishwasher VENT ASMY, BLOWER ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 8 Reviews PartSelect Number PS12741853 Manufacturer Part Number 5304523304 This part is located behind the kickplate. The blower vent assembly opens during the drying cycle to release moisture.

installationInstructions.author: charles from Buxton, ME
installationInstructions.title: UO error - vent open
installationInstructions.content: Pulled out the dishwasher - Located the vent assembly part - unpluged the wiring harness - installed new vent on top of washer plugged in the harness - disconnected the water supply as I had to adjust the rear left leg. Once done I reconnected the water supply and repositioned the dishwasher. WA-LA once installed problem solved.No more washing by hand.
